{
  "texts": [
    "Ahmed et al. [39] provide a comprehensive overview of various 3D representations, discuss DL methods for each representation and compare algorithms based on certain datasets.",
    "Liu et al. [40] focus on feature learning methods for point clouds and analyze their advantages and disadvantages, including the three basic vision tasks and corresponding datasets.",
    "In [41], Vinodkumar et al., present a review of DL-based tasks for 3D point clouds, including segmentation, detection, and classification.",
    "Evaluation performance is reported, as well as the used datasets.",
    "Ioannidou et al. [42] survey methods that apply DL on 3D data and classify them according to the way the input data is treated before being inserted into the DL models."
  ]
}